WEBVTT

00:03:59.440 --> 00:04:02.060
eintlik was hy eerlikwaar oral vier.

00:04:02.060 --> 00:04:03.380
(Gelag)

00:04:03.380 --> 00:04:06.470
Strenggesproke, waarookal hy gegaan het, 
was hy vier daai jaar.

00:04:06.470 --> 00:04:09.660
Hy was in die Kersspel.
Onthou julle die storie?

00:04:09.660 --> 00:04:10.870
(Gelag)

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:12.660
Dit was ’n grote.

00:04:12.660 --> 00:04:15.010
Mel Gibson het die opvolg gedoen.

00:04:15.010 --> 00:04:16.330
(Gelag)

00:04:16.330 --> 00:04:17.650
"Kersspel II."

00:04:19.190 --> 00:04:21.710
James was Josef;
ons was in ons noppies.

00:04:21.710 --> 00:04:25.130
Een van die hoofrolle!

00:04:25.130 --> 00:04:27.080
Ons't agente met T-hemde gehad:

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:29.910
"James Robinson IS Josef!" (Gelag)

00:04:29.910 --> 00:04:31.540
Hy moes niks sê nie, 
maar julle weet mos,